-- Bechtel Interested in Bid to Build LNG Plant in Fujairah
-- B y   A y e s h a   D a y a
-- 2012-09-01T07:10:29Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-09-01/bechtel-interested-in-bid-to-build-lng-plant-in-fujairah.html
Bechtel Group Inc. is “very
interested” in bidding to build a liquefied natural gas plant
in the United Arab Emirates sheikdom of Fujairah, its regional
president for Europe, Africa and the Middle East said today.  The company has built LNG plants all over the world,  David Welch  told reporters in Abu Dhabi. The Fujairah project is being
developed by International Petroleum Investment Co. and Mubadala
Development Co.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ayesha Daya in Dubai at 
 adaya1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
